graph TB
    subgraph "KServe Operator"
        Controller[kserve-controller-manager<br/>Go Operator<br/>Port: 8081/healthz, 8080/metrics]
        Webhook[kserve-webhook-server<br/>Go Webhook Server<br/>Port: 9443/HTTPS TLS1.2+]
        Controller -->|co-located| Webhook
    end

    subgraph "InferenceService Components"
        Agent[kserve-agent<br/>Go Sidecar<br/>Model pulling, logging, batching]
        Router[kserve-router<br/>Go Router<br/>InferenceGraph routing]
        StorageInit[storage-initializer<br/>Python Init Container<br/>Downloads from S3/GCS/Azure]
        ModelServer[Model Servers<br/>Python<br/>sklearn/xgboost/lgb/paddle]

        StorageInit -->|initializes| ModelServer
        Agent -.->|sidecar| ModelServer
    end

    subgraph "Custom Resources"
        InferenceService[InferenceService<br/>serving.kserve.io/v1beta1]
        ServingRuntime[ServingRuntime<br/>serving.kserve.io/v1alpha1]
        ClusterServingRuntime[ClusterServingRuntime<br/>serving.kserve.io/v1alpha1]
        InferenceGraph[InferenceGraph<br/>serving.kserve.io/v1alpha1]
        TrainedModel[TrainedModel<br/>serving.kserve.io/v1alpha1]
    end

    User[User/Data Scientist] -->|creates| InferenceService
    InferenceService -->|validated by| Webhook
    InferenceService -->|reconciled by| Controller

    Controller -->|watches| InferenceService
    Controller -->|watches| ServingRuntime
    Controller -->|watches| ClusterServingRuntime
    Controller -->|watches| InferenceGraph
    Controller -->|watches| TrainedModel

    Controller -->|creates| KnativeService[Knative Service<br/>serverless deployment]
    Controller -->|creates| IstioVS[Istio VirtualService<br/>traffic routing]
    Controller -->|creates| K8sDeploy[Kubernetes Deployment<br/>raw mode]

    subgraph "External Dependencies"
        Knative[Knative Serving 0.39.3<br/>Serverless autoscaling]
        Istio[Istio 1.19.4<br/>Service mesh, mTLS]
        CertManager[cert-manager<br/>TLS certificate mgmt]
        Prometheus[Prometheus<br/>Metrics collection]
    end

    Controller -->|integrates| Knative
    Controller -->|integrates| Istio
    Webhook -->|TLS certs from| CertManager
    ModelServer -->|exposes metrics| Prometheus

    subgraph "Internal ODH/RHOAI"
        ModelRegistry[Model Registry<br/>Model metadata]
        S3Storage[S3 Storage<br/>Model artifacts]
        ServiceMesh[Service Mesh<br/>Istio sidecars]
    end

    Controller -.->|references| ModelRegistry
    StorageInit -->|downloads from| S3Storage
    IstioVS -.->|managed by| ServiceMesh

    style Controller fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Webhook fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
